  <official_title>A Phase 2/3, Randomized, Open-Label, Multi-center Study to Determine the Safety and Efficacy of Solithromycin in Adolescents (12 to 17 Years of Age, Inclusive) and Children (≥2 Months to &lt;12 Years of Age) With Suspected or Confirmed Community-Acquired Bacterial Pneumonia</official_title>
